attributes.description: Gabriel India is part of ANAND Group. The Company has established a significant presence across all automotive customer segments, including OEMs, Aftermarket, and exports. Company manufactures over 500 models of ride control products. [1] Its products include shock absorbers, struts, front forks and others.[2]
